Subject: [PATCH 175/181] f2fs: relax sanity check if checkpoint is corrupted

1. extent_cache
 - let's drop the largest extent_cache
2. invalidate_block
 - don't show the warnings

Signed-off-by: Jaegeuk Kim <jaegeuk@kernel.org>
---
